<task id="005" project="sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix">
  <metadata>
    <title>Coordinate baseline window with `ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r1` (UQ-04)</title>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <estimated-effort>30 minutes</estimated-effort>
    <assigned>Project owner</assigned>
    <started></started>
    <completed></completed>
    <tags>coordination, phase-0</tags>
    <parallel-group>A</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>true</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Independent owner coordination ask</parallel-reason>
    <rigor>STANDARD</rigor>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    Two distinct deliverables:

    1. **Baseline timing coordination (original UQ-04)**: Confirm with the `ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r1` project owner WHEN Phase 1 integration is expected to land in `Sprk.Bff.Api`. This project's Phase 3 baseline must be captured EITHER fully BEFORE the Insights Engine integration starts OR fully AFTER it is stable — never mid-integration (would invalidate App Insights baseline metrics).

    2. **Facade adoption agreement (senior-review G4 / item #4, 2026-05-24)**: Obtain WRITTEN agreement that Insights Engine PRs merging AFTER Phase 4 task 046 (facade creation) MUST consume `Services/Ai/PublicContracts/` facade interfaces rather than injecting `IOpenAiClient` / `IPlaybookService` directly. Belt-and-suspenders to FR-C6 CI gate (lands in Phase 6 task 082); during the gap between task 046 and task 082, this written agreement is the only thing preventing Insights Engine's new code from violating Outcome E.
  </prompt>

  <role>Project coordinator.</role>

  <goal>
    Two documented agreements:
    (a) Baseline window choice: pre-integration OR post-stable; specific calendar window reserved for Phase 3 task 033.
    (b) Insights Engine facade adoption commitment for any PR merged after Phase 4 task 046.
  </goal>

  <inputs>
    <file purpose="design-spec">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/design.md</file>
    <file purpose="sibling-project">projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r1/</file>
    <file purpose="insights-arch">docs/architecture/INSIGHTS-ENGINE-ARCHITECTURE.md</file>
  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="design.md §2.3">Capture Phase 3 baseline BEFORE Engine integration starts, OR fully AFTER stable</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r1/README.md</file>
      <file>docs/architecture/INSIGHTS-ENGINE-ARCHITECTURE.md</file>
      <file>projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/design.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <context>
    <background>
      Insights Engine Phase 1 integrates ~5 services + new index code INTO `Sprk.Bff.Api`. That
      adds size and changes App Insights signal characteristics. If our 48h baseline is captured
      mid-integration, Phase 4 will compare against a noisy reference, undermining the regression
      detection. Engine project is currently pre-implementation (design phase), so there is
      flexibility.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency task="001" status="not-started">Owner sign-off required first</dependency>
    </dependencies>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Contact `ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r1` owner</step>
    <step order="2">Confirm Phase 1 integration target dates</step>
    <step order="3">Choose baseline window: pre-integration OR post-stable</step>
    <step order="4">Obtain WRITTEN agreement that any Insights Engine PR merged after this project's Phase 4 task 046 uses `Services/Ai/PublicContracts/` facade interfaces — NOT direct injection of `IOpenAiClient`/`IPlaybookService` (senior review G4)</step>
    <step order="5">Record both decisions (baseline window + facade adoption commitment) in CLAUDE.md → Decisions Made</step>
    <step order="6">Update Phase 0 checklist item 4 to checked</step>
    <step order="7">Update TASK-INDEX.md status of task 005 from 🔲 to ✅</step>
  </steps>

  <tools><tool name="git">Update CLAUDE.md + task index</tool></tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="docs">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/CLAUDE.md (Decisions Made entry)</output>
    <output type="docs">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/tasks/TASK-INDEX.md (status update)</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">UQ-04 answer recorded with scheduled baseline window</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Written facade-adoption agreement recorded for Insights Engine PRs post-task-046 (G4)</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Phase 0 checklist item 4 marked complete</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
